thread.title: sophie

author: sophie
title: sophie
text: I always have such a positive experience with this company. They cards always look great, are packaged well, and i usually receive them within 3 days of placing my order. The only negative I could say is sometimes I wish I could alter more without writing to the company but this is such a small thing that it doesn't really affect my choice, and for easy, affordable and professional looking invites paper divas are always my 'go to'.
